  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Popup Box"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Reference Geometry</text> is a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">sketch-element</text> that we copy onto the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Base-Part</text> in the active <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text> from a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text> in a different <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor.</text> If you edit or move the source sketch-element, the <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Reference Geometry</text> in the active <text styleclass="Popup Box2">Mechanism-Editor</text> also updates to the new size or position. <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Reference-Geometry</text> updates dynamically through a machine-cycle.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
